org.geppetto.model.datasources

Interface CompoundRefQuery

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISynchable, Node, Query
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompoundRefQueryImpl

    public interface CompoundRefQuery
extends Query
    A representation of the model object 'Compound Ref Query'. Compound ref queries make it possible to reference queries from any datasource

    The following features are supported:

    • Query Chain
    See Also:
    DatasourcesPackage.getCompoundRefQuery()
